title.rendered: Aeroflo O2/ Oxygen Face Mask with Tube

content.rendered:
Face masks are used to deliver oxygen to people who don’t otherwise get enough of it. They are commonly used to provide relief to people with respiratory disorders.

Face masks are usually used to deliver low levels of oxygen to the patient.
